  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d8e16fd1-624c-4cff-84f9-4750dba4712d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d8e16fd1-624c-4cff-84f9-4750dba4712d\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2aa6ab1d62ed16bb.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"567\", \"originalHeight\" : \"567\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2aa6ab1d62ed16bb.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2aa6ab1d62ed16bb.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87a28a92-5319-4710-b34d-3afbea5faaa5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a6c10902-a9ed-45a9-a323-0da907fb519d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-47d603c4-7266-47a3-8be5-fc4b156654ea\">모두 건강히 잘 지내고 계신지요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8861ed91-f0e4-459b-96c4-e22f0eb6a627\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-67337c6d-fe27-4171-8136-96e4b7516675\">코로나19 확산세가 꺽이지 않고 연일 300명대를 넘나드는 확진자들이 나오면서 외출 삼가와 집에서의 생활이 권장되고 있습니다. 특히 30일 0시를 기준으로 사회적 거리두기가 2.5단계로 상향되면서 당분간은 집에서의 생활을 이어 나가야할 상황입니다.</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-44576276-f12d-47a8-a210-de4be376a5b6\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-573f8ffa-2d1c-4223-a0f3-480c80e0779a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c8a2111e-0b5f-4f1c-873f-4d5abfb27335\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3e33f29-a053-4263-8b2d-0b6da736bba3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d3e33f29-a053-4263-8b2d-0b6da736bba3\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2a0e31b7603ee715.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"640\", \"originalHeight\" : \"420\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2a0e31b7603ee715.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2a0e31b7603ee715.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"328\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1b11c1c1-64e9-4da2-aa3d-c0e18c3f046e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1306dfac-d0ad-4e38-b4e3-69359a1661ed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aa21ef3c-49f1-4cb0-8f1e-8aebfa6eca37\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5502881c-4385-4fda-8411-8ee92856187e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae5b0090-5e0c-4fa5-ac6b-8f4fd7e79a36\">이런 사회적 거리두기로 인해 많은 분들이 힘들어하고 있지만 특히 학교에 가지 못하고 집에서 온라인 강의를 들어야 하는 학생들이 많이 힘들어하고 있습니다. 한참 친구들과 어울리고 열심히 공부해야 할 학생들이 야외활동을 거의 하지 못하고 집에서 오랜 시간 PC앞에 앉아 있게 되면서 여러가지 증상을 호소하는 경우가 늘어나고 있습니다. 또한 공부에 힘을 기울여야할 수험생들이 체력적으로 힘들어하면서 부모님들이 한의원에 데리고 오는 경우가 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5d6588b3-3d38-4d77-a22b-078c3c2d4bc0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-5d6588b3-3d38-4d77-a22b-078c3c2d4bc0\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2d603c6695e7a9cc.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"800\", \"originalHeight\" : \"450\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2d603c6695e7a9cc.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2d603c6695e7a9cc.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"281\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d61b90d9-90f1-4b4e-988a-539b753a69ae\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ecede480-3161-4fb1-b323-198d9622ad28\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-eb48f2f5-69cf-4b6f-a958-5dcab5ec4caf\">코로나 19때문에 학교는 가지 못하지만 공부를 놓을 수 없는 아이들이 오랜 시간 PC로 학습을 하게 되면서 아래와 같은 증상들이 많이 발생하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-fcd455f2-0bd1-4015-8789-676583a2d950\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5313d672-b51c-4afa-a925-e6397adf3f4a\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-661da592-0d4a-4542-a3fc-1bd930a71738\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-16007e8d-261f-4b0c-b95f-85939249f72a\"><u> 오래 PC를 하게 되면서 어깨가 굳고 머리가 멍하여 집중이 안 되는 경우:</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3376c9dd-acfc-4900-9b77-701c3ae27894\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b35a24cf-e33c-4437-bdef-61559f771799\">어깨 근육을 풀어주어 두뇌로의 기혈 순환을 원활하게 해주는 한약처방과 물리치료를 병행</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-252d5871-5c89-490c-9f62-876db055d9cd\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-db0eb1c6-d9bd-4b21-9742-4407341375e1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ba7763aa-cf31-4312-be37-0b5942d79526\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-69bbadda-d510-494b-8469-8b876227efbd\">2. </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-02002db6-13af-4cab-81e3-6a4dc4a8361e\"><u>활동량이 줄어들면서 체중이 늘고 체력이 떨어진 경우:</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-737e975f-498c-4755-b4d3-79d77b81cc92\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b5aadbbd-c4d7-4281-8a7f-d53475b31769\">몸을 무겁게 하는 노폐물을 배출시키고 심폐의 기능을 높혀 활력을 생기게 해 주는 한약처방과 침치료 병행</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-71575492-4da3-449f-9a26-0c62a6e3e690\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-64d76c6f-ba23-4564-8b6f-67582400e745\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cf49684b-e9f7-4ca4-9eb7-72c824af1ac1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5a1d938b-a4e4-49c6-8db6-e300a885902f\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b7a0b639-b289-42f7-aa9d-8f9ed3632343\"><u> 식욕이 줄고 기운이 떨어진 경우:</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-68da9a8f-54ad-46a7-a073-df13f04444dd\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-90f4803b-0c9a-406e-8b84-d3d747cd95e9\">소화기를 좋게 하고 활력이 생기게 해주는 한약 처방</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e8ca5d66-621a-43f1-bd98-dc47a0634ae5\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5c2a3c7a-1aa1-4893-bd5d-6a0b667624da\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d96cd97-0b18-4cce-b880-83acfb74494f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-cb8edfdd-7072-43a7-be26-77bb48b93e6b\">4. </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-4fee1a94-a72a-4a19-8f66-a09e114ad5dd\"><u>시력이 떨어지고 눈이 피로하다고 호소하는 경우:</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-655185cf-bdad-4cee-8cb4-39c90b5cff69\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-07548e22-9fbf-4fa8-a33b-c1d4902e0a80\">시력이 더 이상 떨어지지 않도록 혈기를 돕고 순환을 좋게 하는 한약 처방과 침치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-090b60af-f3e2-4574-817e-708cb9a384ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b2102759-fad4-4d11-8707-e69acf191b8b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-489d14a4-1e40-41b5-be42-c274a1ad300c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-6548b698-3f06-4ee2-8655-d2aa9cf55884\">5. </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-cc0bb7e7-80d0-4922-b9b1-0c648e4e63ee\"><u>열심히 공부해야 하는데 자꾸 졸리는 경우:</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e1514c8c-3355-4256-955f-da08aabbb343\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3faa2d30-06e6-4b0c-a1e8-117792704059\">기혈이 부족하여 자꾸 졸린 경우에는 기혈보강과 총명해질 수 있도록 돕는 한약처방</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-18dc28a6-23fa-43d5-8409-e537bb0b8e38\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-37410359-8d33-44ed-9124-ac8531043f6f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-becd2add-9de4-40a5-95d6-0aeadabbc364\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-a2a0cb8c-5ca6-4180-9b1e-29253f4f123c\">6.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-2bb97c21-e636-48f1-bb09-da2072d3b631\"><u> 잠을 푹 자지 못하고 예민한 경우:</u></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-98627fa7-9a38-4a43-a898-a4dd69841113\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b626fb6a-5608-42b0-b1d8-84f2cc2a851f\">심신을 안정시켜 푹 자고 예민함이 덜해질 수 있는 한약 처방</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a1f3da3c-58f7-418a-9a42-1d111417cf12\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-590982ce-ba4b-4931-8a71-ab5264991640\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd229281-48d7-49a7-a635-07219ff05dd1\">이수한의원에서는 소아청소년과 진료 경험이 많은 나효석 원장님이 체질에 따라</span><span style=\"background-color:#fff593;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3d1146d8-2f96-400e-b3b7-d1782bcfc93a\"> </span><span style=\"background-color:#fff593;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-96d798f4-1c3e-408e-9cd5-6360bbbfa862\"><u>맞춤처방과 공진단, 총명탕</u></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4f821ac5-5d8c-4b75-bab5-1a12ad460deb\">을 처방해 수험생, 어린이들이 더욱 건강해질 수 있도록 도와드리고 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7625573d-3d4c-49a8-8d3e-094358651a80\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-302ec037-5b3d-47ba-873f-56a04f283a8d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-39132dce-6fdd-4854-b85b-dc5c185240cc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4b2ba92d-a0a8-42b0-924a-41a404a80756\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
